Predict values from Ridge regression

predict_ridge.Rd

Predict values from Ridge regression

predict_ridge(obj, newx, cv = TRUE)

Arguments

newx

Value

Examples



n <- 100 ; p <- 10
X <- matrix(rnorm(n * p), n, p) # no intercept!
y <- rnorm(n)

fit_obj <- ahead::fit_ridge(X, y)

n_test <- 10

predict_ridge(fit_obj, newx=matrix(rnorm(n_test * p), n_test, p),
cv=TRUE)
